<mvc:View controllerName="gourmeo.resources.main.controllers.NewReviewItem" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" 
    xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form"
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">

    <Page title="{i18n>newItemPageTitle}" id="pageNewItem" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress">
        <content>
            <VBox class="sapUiSmallMargin">
                <f:SimpleForm editable="true" layout="ResponsiveGridLayout" labelSpanXL="3" labelSpanL="3" labelSpanM="3" labelSpanS="12" adjustLabelSpan="false" emptySpanXL="4" emptySpanL="4" emptySpanM="4" emptySpanS="0" columnsXL="1" columnsL="1" columnsM="1" singleContainerFullSize="false">
                    <f:content>
                        <core:Title text="{i18n>newItemFormHeaderGen}" />
                        <Label text="{i18n>newItemDescription}" />
                        <Input required="true" change="onItemDescChange" id="txtNewItemDesc" />
                        <Label text="{i18n>newItemPrice}" />
                        <Input description="{i18n>newItemCurrency}" id="txtNewItemPrice" />
                        <Label text="{i18n>newItemExternalId}" />
                        <Input id="txtExternalId" />
                        <core:Title text="{i18n>newItemFormHeaderMakers}" />
                        <Label text="{i18n>newItemResponsible}" />
                        <Input id="txtNewItemRespo" />
                        <Label text="{i18n>newItemAuxiliary}" />
                        <Input id="txtNewItemAux" />
                    </f:content>
                </f:SimpleForm>
            </VBox>
        </content>
        <footer>
            <Toolbar>
                <content>
                    <ToolbarSpacer />
                    <Button type="Emphasized" text="{i18n>btnSave}" press="onSaveItemPress" />
                </content>
            </Toolbar>
        </footer>
    </Page>

</mvc:View>